<body>

   

    <div class="recipe-container">
        <h1>Soft and Fluffy Idly Recipe</h1>
      

        <h2>Ingredients:</h2>
        <ul class="ingredients-list">
            <li>2 cups Idly Rice</li>
            <li>1 cup Urad Dal (Black Gram Lentils)</li>
            <li>1/2 tsp Fenugreek Seeds</li>
            <li>Salt to taste</li>
            <li>Water as required</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Instructions:</h2>
        <ol class="instructions-list">
            <li>Soak idly rice and urad dal (with fenugreek seeds) separately for 6 hours.</li>
            <li>Grind urad dal to a smooth batter and then grind rice to a coarse batter.</li>
            <li>Mix both batters, add salt, and let it ferment overnight.</li>
            <li>Grease idly plates, pour batter, and steam for 10-12 minutes.</li>
            <li>Serve hot with coconut chutney and sambar.</li>
        </ol>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
